# browser-harness

Always use `browser-harness` for web interaction: automation, scraping, testing, or site/app work.

- Setup or connection issues: read `.cursor/skills/browser-harness/install.md`.
- UI mechanics (dialogs, tabs, iframes, uploads): read `.cursor/skills/browser-harness/interaction-skills/`.
- First navigation uses `new_tab(url)`, not `goto_url(url)`.
- If local Chrome blocks CDP: enable remote debugging at `chrome://inspect/#remote-debugging`.
